2018 MIDDLE SCHOOL NATIONAL SPEECH & DEBATE TOURNAMENT
We certify that EACH above named contestant is a student at this middle school and-while attending the
Middle School National Speech & Debate Tournament-will be under the supervision of the supervising
adult signing this form, who is the student's parent, coach, or school administrator, approved by the
school principal, and staying at the same lodging as the student(s) they are supervising.
Note: If the supervising adult and coach is the same person, SIGN AS BOTH Supervising Adult AND Coach.
